{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"他們靠在床上注視著，"},{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"「不信道的人們已獲得他們的行為的報酬了嗎？」"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"當天綻裂，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"聽從主命，而且宜於聽從的時候；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"當地展開，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"並拋其所懷，而且變為空虛，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"聽從主命，而且宜於聽從的時候；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人啊！你必定勉力工作，直到會見你的主，你將看到自己的勞績。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"至於用右手接過功過簿者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"將受簡易的稽核，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"而興高采烈地返於他的家屬；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"至於從背後接受功過簿者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"將叫苦連天，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"入於烈火之中，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"從前他在家屬間原是快樂的，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他已猜想他絕不會歸於主。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"不然，他的主，原是鑒察他的。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我以晚霞盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"以黑夜及其包羅萬象的盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"以圓滿時的月亮盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你們必定遭遇重重的災難。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他們怎能不信道呢？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"當別人對他們宣讀《古蘭經》的時候，他們怎麼不叩頭呢？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"不然，不信道的人們，是否認真理的，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"真主全知道他們心中隱藏的東西，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"故你當以一種痛苦的刑罰向他們報喜，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"惟信道而且行善的人們，將受不斷的報酬。"}]}